CATEGORIES:Talks,MAP,CBD
DTSTAMP:20260407T060552Z
DESCRIPTION:Join artist afra eisma\, in conversation with Dr. Gita Chadha and unpack the making of warrior garments. Explore the ideas contained within the artworks\, what it means to centre sexual violence and personal trauma through art\, and the precarity of talking about it across nations and institutions. Discover the contours of afra’s practice\, the people and art that inspires them\, and the hope they carry for the future in these dark times. 
DTEND:20260412T123000Z
DTSTART:20260412T110000Z
SUMMARY:In Focus: afra eisma
UID:1243@map-india.org
URL:https://map-india.org/map-events/in-focus-afra-eisma/
END:VEVENT
